#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><p>
#: en/faq.xml:229
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You don't need to redo every step of the installation, but investigating the\n"
"kernel and all associated steps is necessary. Suppose you have installed Gentoo\n"
